&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, January 26 (KCNA) --The U.S. Group for the Study of the Songun Politics opened a special Internet homepage on Jan. 1 to praise the great Songun policy.
 Posted on the homepage are an article praising the historic long journey of Songun made by leader Kim Jong Il contributed by John Paul Cupp, chairman of the group, articles introducing the essence and vitality of the policy and nearly 20 photos titled �gSongun history seen through photos�h. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The chairman in his article said Kim Jong Il has resolutely defied the wanton threat and pressure of the U.S. imperialists and reactionaries with his treasured sword called Songun. He continued: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Recorded in the history are the disgraceful defeats the great sun of Songun has inflicted upon the imperialists. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Korean socialism has stood as a fortress defending independence and achieving prosperity, throwing bright rays all over the world, and the cause of Korea�fs reunification and the cause of global independence and the cause against imperialism and the U.S. has dynamically advanced, valiantly meeting all challenges. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
